{"tid":1411174,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"王丹：習帝不敢出兵 共產黨冇共識","createTime":"2019-08-05T03:05:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T03:23:52.000Z","uid":225846,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6d21f9053024e702329c0ac19a96ab638c75a9bb","tid":1411174,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:05:57.000Z","msg":"林鄭開記者會，沒有宣布請求中央政府出兵，但依舊譴責市民，也不肯下台，用不知所謂的&ldquo;以後每日開記者會&rdquo;來搪塞，甚至用經濟衰退來喊話，<br />\n<br />\n這證明我週四的文章的預測是正確的，那就是：<br />\n<br />\n至少到目前為止，習近平還是不敢出兵，但又不甘心讓步，中共內部一定也還沒有取得共識，於是北京還是希望港府自己解決，但是港府也一籌莫展。結果就是這樣：出來講了一堆廢話，有講跟沒講一樣。香港人的堅持和勇氣，令北京和港府都束手無策，進退兩難。<br />\n<br />\n香港人民太偉大了。<br />\n<br />\n香港加油！香港撐住！"},{"pid":"25adfbaf73f10a35b04d902847d8a0cd00899b48","tid":1411174,"uid":260367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:11:55.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0294019ac3416e65ac44672b8a2ec56c1f2e555f","tid":1411174,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:12:59.000Z","msg":"link?"},{"pid":"539b65122ff66ce2748aa1f972c7fd317704a90d","tid":1411174,"uid":202577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:14:42.000Z","msg":"非你係武裝革命，如果唔係無乜條件出兵"},{"pid":"abb473ff159ed74f5127980b53be6557ac16920c","tid":1411174,"uid":35914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:14:54.000Z","msg":"王丹係咪入唔到香港境？"},{"pid":"9a1a244f410498de465c3b59a0d13f3c7b39ea1d","tid":1411174,"uid":61280,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:15:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">老實，又唔好支那DNA打過分飛機，支共唔出兵都只係怯美帝囉！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n從來歷史話你知，支那種政權攞你自己人條命洗驚？？？！！！</span></span></span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"075616dc0f29cf00f3000b2643ddf607529cbc52","tid":1411174,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,